OL,4,CLeasehold campaigners welcome new
OL,5,Cchanges
OL,6, Two big players in the leasehold sector
OL,7, have agreed to change the way they
OL,8, operate, following an investigation by
OL,9, the competition watchdog.
OL,11,FHousebuilder Persimmon will allow its
OL,12,Fleaseholders to buy the freehold of
OL,13,Ftheir property at a discount.
OL,15,FInsurance company Aviva, which buys
OL,16,Fleaseholds from house builders, will
OL,17,Frepay homeowners who saw their ground
OL,18,Frents double.
OL,20,FCampaigners for leaseholders said the
OL,21,Fcommitments were a "massive milestone".
